<h3 id="mutant">"mutant"</h3>

<p>November 2021, Procreate for iPad. Another mermaid painting. When approached to make cover art for <a href="/work/mutants">Mutants Mixtape</a>, my first thought was "just make it a picture of a mutant"... which, amazingly, they hadn't done yet. The rest is self-explanatory.</p>

