<h3 id="futa-angel-nsfw">"futa angel" (nsfw)</h3>

<p>October 2021, Clip Studio Paint for Mac. Uh... I don't know how to describe this one without sounding disgusting. I'm kind of obsessed with the idea of appropriating hentai tropes in my art... I like to play around with the trope of "futanari" â€” meaning "two kinds"; basically hermaphrodite girls with dicks â€” and use it as an expression of my transness, rather than the crude fetishization it usually is.</p>

