<h3 id="red-sun">"red sun"</h3>

<p>February 2021, Clip Studio Paint for Mac. Style exploration for my manga <a href="/work/mm">MM</a>. I was imagining an irradiated world post climate change, where the sun paints the hazy sky around it a bright red.</p>

